title: Ethereum’s Holesky Testnet Fails To Launch, in Rare Tech Misstep for the Blockchain
description: Developers of the Ethereum blockchain say there was a misconfiguration in the genesis files of the test network, and now they plan to try again in about two weeks.

title: FTX Restores Full Access to Claims Portal After Cybersecurity Breach
description: The portal allowing FTX customers to file claims with the bankrupt cryptocurrency exchange is again fully operational after a recent security incident. User accounts that were affected by the breach in August have been unfrozen, the failed crypto trading company announced.
